magpie.csp

Class CompositionBasedCSPEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • magpie.csp.CSPEngine
      • magpie.csp.CompositionBasedCSPEngine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Commandable, Options, Printable

    public class CompositionBasedCSPEngine
extends CSPEngine
    Use machine learning model trained on the composition of the entries. Usage: $<model template>
    model template: Template of a BaseClassifier used to predict which structure is most likely

    Implemented Commands:

    attributes [<command...>] - Configure how attributes are generated
    command: Attribute command from PrototypeDataset
